1
00:01:31,330 --> 00:01:35,000
[Wind Direction]

2
00:01:35,470 --> 00:01:37,800
[Episode 6]

3
00:01:38,110 --> 00:01:39,150
Hang in there.

4
00:01:39,170 --> 00:01:42,330
[Summer of the Year 1987]

5
00:01:44,780 --> 00:01:45,330
Well,

6
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:47,440
why does Lei's son

7
00:01:47,470 --> 00:01:49,030
behave like a girl?

8
00:01:49,030 --> 00:01:50,070
He even scratched others.

9
00:01:50,070 --> 00:01:51,640
Look at the wound.

10
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:53,289
You only know how to tell on him.

11
00:01:53,289 --> 00:01:55,150
Fight back if you dare.

12
00:01:56,509 --> 00:01:58,270
I'm a reserve of the young pioneers.

13
00:01:58,270 --> 00:02:00,910
I have to be civilized and not fight with others.

14
00:02:00,910 --> 00:02:01,750
You're right.

15
00:02:02,870 --> 00:02:03,350
Miaomiao,

16
00:02:03,350 --> 00:02:04,520
what did I tell you?

17
00:02:04,930 --> 00:02:07,050
Be reasonable when conflicts arise.

18
00:02:07,300 --> 00:02:08,030
Even if you win a fight,

19
00:02:08,030 --> 00:02:09,750
does that mean you're in the right?

20
00:02:09,750 --> 00:02:11,880
Does crying all the time make it right?

21
00:02:11,910 --> 00:02:12,510
Son,

22
00:02:13,110 --> 00:02:14,190
listen to me.

23
00:02:14,430 --> 00:02:15,470
If anyone dares to bully you in the future,

24
00:02:15,470 --> 00:02:16,360
fight back.

25
00:02:16,540 --> 00:02:17,350
If you beat them a few more times,

26
00:02:17,350 --> 00:02:19,090
no one will dare to bully you anymore.

27
00:02:19,090 --> 00:02:21,220
Why are you heightening the conflict?

28
00:02:21,230 --> 00:02:22,670
Also, the kids may be out of line

29
00:02:22,670 --> 00:02:23,470
when fighting.

30
00:02:23,470 --> 00:02:24,650
What if he hurts them badly?

31
00:02:24,650 --> 00:02:26,380
Won't the parents look for you?

32
00:02:26,470 --> 00:02:27,790
It's between the kids.

33
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:29,150
They can solve it themselves.

34
00:02:29,150 --> 00:02:30,760
Parents shouldn't get involved.

35
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:31,360
No, you...

36
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,550
Son, does it hurt?

37
00:02:35,150 --> 00:02:35,880
Does it hurt?

38
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:37,730
Let me give you a hug.

39
00:02:37,829 --> 00:02:38,630
Let me hug you.

40
00:02:41,670 --> 00:02:44,350
[Don't Leave After School]

41
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,650
Why are you standing there?

42
00:02:48,110 --> 00:02:49,770
Go back and call your parents.

43
00:02:49,820 --> 00:02:50,740
Mr. Gao,

44
00:02:51,350 --> 00:02:52,630
I'm the victim.

45
00:02:52,630 --> 00:02:54,110
He started it.

46
00:02:54,260 --> 00:02:55,390
He kicked me

47
00:02:55,390 --> 00:02:56,579
and I knelt on the floor.

48
00:02:56,579 --> 00:02:57,610
It was too sudden.

49
00:03:01,350 --> 00:03:02,550
Why didn't he kick me?

50
00:03:02,740 --> 00:03:04,050
If he dares to kick you,

51
00:03:04,190 --> 00:03:05,650
we should call the police.

52
00:03:05,890 --> 00:03:07,130
Cut the crap.

53
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:08,740
Why did he kick you?

54
00:03:09,020 --> 00:03:10,080
You have to ask him.

55
00:03:10,590 --> 00:03:11,460
Everyone saw him

56
00:03:11,460 --> 00:03:12,210
kick me.

57
00:03:12,410 --> 00:03:13,410
I have witnesses.

58
00:03:14,170 --> 00:03:16,250
Mr. Gao, my leg

59
00:03:16,270 --> 00:03:17,360
is bruised now.

60
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:19,440
It doesn't look serious,

61
00:03:19,590 --> 00:03:20,670
but it's a joint.

62
00:03:20,670 --> 00:03:21,750
I'm having an internal injury.

63
00:03:21,750 --> 00:03:23,280
It's hard for me to walk now.

64
00:03:23,340 --> 00:03:24,670
I can't even stand well.

65
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:26,470
Fine.

66
00:03:27,190 --> 00:03:28,110
Sit here.

67
00:03:28,110 --> 00:03:29,670
No, no, no.

68
00:03:29,670 --> 00:03:30,579
Have a seat.

69
00:03:30,610 --> 00:03:31,440
I can hold on.

70
00:03:34,310 --> 00:03:35,110
Qiang Xiaowa.

71
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,480
You didn't say a word.

72
00:03:37,740 --> 00:03:39,670
Does it have nothing to do with you?

73
00:03:42,230 --> 00:03:43,430
I don't have parents.

74
00:03:47,990 --> 00:03:48,880
No parents?

75
00:03:49,390 --> 00:03:50,720
What about your family?

76
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,190
I'm sorry.

77
00:03:58,579 --> 00:04:00,900
What do you mean?

78
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:01,950
Mr. Gao, did you hear that?

79
00:04:01,950 --> 00:04:02,830
He apologized to me.

80
00:04:02,830 --> 00:04:04,170
I'm really a victim.

81
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:06,430
He hit me on purpose.

82
00:04:06,460 --> 00:04:08,430
Sir, no one hit Li Si.

83
00:04:09,090 --> 00:04:10,770
It was a misunderstanding.

84
00:04:11,740 --> 00:04:13,620
Sir, we were just kidding.

85
00:04:13,640 --> 00:04:15,360
Li Si said he knows Shaolin kung fu.

86
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,339
So we had a battle.

87
00:04:16,339 --> 00:04:17,269
Qiang Xiaowa knocked Li Si down

88
00:04:17,269 --> 00:04:18,990
when he tried to get up.

89
00:04:19,029 --> 00:04:20,029
Li Si is a petty person

90
00:04:20,029 --> 00:04:21,370
who loves to talk nonsense.

91
00:04:21,370 --> 00:04:23,170
Don't take his words seriously.

92
00:04:23,270 --> 00:04:24,430
Cheng Miaomiao,

93
00:04:25,450 --> 00:04:27,010
why do you betray me again?

94
00:04:29,190 --> 00:04:30,390
Call the parents if you want.

95
00:04:30,390 --> 00:04:31,070
Your dad will definitely

96
00:04:31,070 --> 00:04:32,400
uphold justice for you.

97
00:04:33,580 --> 00:04:34,750
No need.

98
00:04:34,860 --> 00:04:36,350
My dad is at the front line now.

99
00:04:36,350 --> 00:04:37,650
He won't be back for a while.

100
00:04:37,650 --> 00:04:38,800
Oh yeah.

101
00:04:38,830 --> 00:04:39,500
You're right.

102
00:04:39,500 --> 00:04:41,550
I was just kidding.

103
00:04:41,710 --> 00:04:43,170
I hit the table corner by myself

104
00:04:43,170 --> 00:04:44,900
and knelt there accidentally.

105
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:46,010
It was a misunderstanding.

106
00:04:46,010 --> 00:04:47,210
A misunderstanding.

107
00:04:52,390 --> 00:04:53,450
You can work harder

108
00:04:53,550 --> 00:04:54,930
if you're not good at studies.

109
00:04:54,930 --> 00:04:56,790
There are many ways to achieve it.

110
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,440
But I don't allow you

111
00:04:58,980 --> 00:05:00,580
to have an attitude problem.

112
00:05:01,830 --> 00:05:02,870
I'll forget

113
00:05:02,890 --> 00:05:04,400
about what happened today,

114
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:06,000
but you know what to do.

115
00:05:06,670 --> 00:05:07,470
Qiang Xiaowa.

116
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:10,430
It's not easy to transfer to a new school.

117
00:05:10,430 --> 00:05:11,440
Break those of your bad habits

118
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:12,570
as soon as possible.

119
00:05:13,110 --> 00:05:13,630
This is the school.

120
00:05:13,630 --> 00:05:16,030
You're not allowed to do whatever you want.

121
00:05:17,400 --> 00:05:18,070
Li Si.

122
00:05:18,830 --> 00:05:20,620
If you don't want to be beaten by your dad,

123
00:05:20,620 --> 00:05:21,850
behave yourself.

124
00:05:22,670 --> 00:05:23,390
As a man,

125
00:05:23,390 --> 00:05:24,670
it's very low-class

126
00:05:24,910 --> 00:05:26,640
to solve problems by fighting.

127
00:05:27,910 --> 00:05:29,040
If you do this again,

128
00:05:29,990 --> 00:05:31,110
I'm sure you two

129
00:05:31,670 --> 00:05:33,530
will leave this school together.

130
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:35,140
Understand?

131
00:05:35,930 --> 00:05:36,420
Yes.

132
00:05:37,470 --> 00:05:38,210
Louder.

133
00:05:38,870 --> 00:05:39,870
Yes!

134
00:05:40,340 --> 00:05:41,240
[Office No. 2]

135
00:05:44,380 --> 00:05:45,310
Cheng Miaomiao,

136
00:05:46,070 --> 00:05:47,790
you're totally a traitor.

137
00:05:47,990 --> 00:05:49,230
You do feel guilty.

138
00:05:49,630 --> 00:05:50,470
He started it.

139
00:05:50,470 --> 00:05:51,670
Why would I feel guilty?

140
00:05:51,670 --> 00:05:52,590
Don't be ungrateful.

141
00:05:52,590 --> 00:05:53,670
I saved you from being beaten up.

142
00:05:53,670 --> 00:05:54,270
Got it?

143
00:05:54,270 --> 00:05:55,270
I'm a victim.

144
00:05:55,270 --> 00:05:56,000
Why would my dad hit me?

145
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:56,870
Why would he believe that

146
00:05:56,870 --> 00:05:57,930
you are the victim?

147
00:05:59,110 --> 00:06:00,000
Qiang Xiaowa.

148
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:00,870
Let's fight outside the school

149
00:06:00,870 --> 00:06:01,910
if you dare.

150
00:06:02,190 --> 00:06:04,150
Do you want a beating that badly?

151
00:06:04,150 --> 00:06:05,240
That's no big deal.

152
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,390
I must avenge myself.

153
00:06:06,390 --> 00:06:08,470
You're going to be beaten twice.

154
00:06:08,630 --> 00:06:09,790
Just now, when you fought with him,

155
00:06:09,790 --> 00:06:10,430
didn't you realize

156
00:06:10,430 --> 00:06:11,390
you came off worse?

157
00:06:11,390 --> 00:06:13,030
That's because he ambushed me.

158
00:06:13,030 --> 00:06:13,870
So I have to take my revenge on him.

159
00:06:13,870 --> 00:06:14,790
Ambushed?

160
00:06:14,790 --> 00:06:15,550
He did.

161
00:06:15,550 --> 00:06:16,110
Don't fight with him.

162
00:06:16,110 --> 00:06:17,270
I fight for you.

163
00:06:17,270 --> 00:06:18,730
Even so, you can't do that.

164
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:21,930
Cheng Yaya.

165
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:26,300
Cheng Yaya, what happened?

166
00:06:26,300 --> 00:06:27,180
Cheng Yaya.

167
00:06:30,770 --> 00:06:31,890
I'm not convinced.

168
00:06:32,390 --> 00:06:32,830
Why could

169
00:06:32,830 --> 00:06:33,550
a wanted man's child

170
00:06:33,550 --> 00:06:34,409
come to school?

171
00:06:34,940 --> 00:06:36,350
Which rule says that

172
00:06:36,370 --> 00:06:37,710
the child of a wanted criminal

173
00:06:37,710 --> 00:06:39,240
has no right to go to school?

174
00:06:40,270 --> 00:06:41,530
They are accomplices.

175
00:06:43,790 --> 00:06:45,390
Did the police tell you that?

176
00:06:47,190 --> 00:06:48,070
Did you fight

177
00:06:48,070 --> 00:06:48,909
for this?

178
00:06:50,730 --> 00:06:52,659
Cheng Yaya, what's wrong with you?

179
00:06:52,980 --> 00:06:54,430
He wanted to beat Yuan Shanqing.

180
00:06:54,430 --> 00:06:55,470
So I stopped him.

181
00:06:56,590 --> 00:06:59,120
Yet he came to take revenge on me after school.

182
00:06:59,909 --> 00:07:01,370
He hit me and I fought back.

183
00:07:02,380 --> 00:07:03,040
Luo Zheng.

184
00:07:03,470 --> 00:07:05,150
The school is not a police station.

185
00:07:05,150 --> 00:07:06,150
It's not your turn

186
00:07:06,150 --> 00:07:07,310
to beat up and arrest the bad guy.

187
00:07:07,310 --> 00:07:07,910
Are you all

188
00:07:07,930 --> 00:07:09,190
indulging the bad guy?

189
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,770
Who on earth is the bad guy here?

190
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:21,460
What are you doing?

191
00:07:21,670 --> 00:07:23,130
Do you want to fight again?

192
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:25,280
Fine.

193
00:07:26,060 --> 00:07:26,640
Fight.

194
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:36,230
Goodbye, teachers.

195
00:07:37,610 --> 00:07:38,340
Yaya.

196
00:07:38,940 --> 00:07:39,980
Why are you here?

197
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:41,970
Where is the guy who hit you?

198
00:07:42,659 --> 00:07:44,260
We were fighting each other.

199
00:07:44,710 --> 00:07:47,470
Look at you, were you two fighting each other?

200
00:07:47,470 --> 00:07:49,110
Obviously he hit you.

201
00:07:49,190 --> 00:07:50,430
His face is swollen.

202
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:51,909
I don't care if his face is swollen.

203
00:07:51,909 --> 00:07:52,790
Where is he?

204
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:55,210
He's writing an apology letter in the office.

205
00:07:55,210 --> 00:07:56,620
What are you going to do?

206
00:07:58,030 --> 00:07:59,159
What am I going to do?

207
00:07:59,670 --> 00:08:00,750
I want him to pay for

208
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:01,780
bullying my brother.

209
00:08:01,780 --> 00:08:03,370
I have to teach him a lesson.

210
00:08:03,940 --> 00:08:05,150
Let me tell you once again.

211
00:08:05,150 --> 00:08:06,510
We were fighting each other.

212
00:08:06,510 --> 00:08:07,910
Mind your own business.

213
00:08:30,710 --> 00:08:31,510
Qiang Xiaowa,

214
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:33,830
you helped us before

215
00:08:33,830 --> 00:08:35,159
and we also thanked you.

216
00:08:35,909 --> 00:08:36,710
Forget it if you don't appreciate it.

217
00:08:36,710 --> 00:08:37,950
But you hit me.

218
00:08:39,659 --> 00:08:40,630
Do you think you can poop on my neck

219
00:08:40,630 --> 00:08:42,159
because you helped me once?

220
00:08:43,630 --> 00:08:45,290
I'll give you two choices now.

221
00:08:45,790 --> 00:08:46,510
First,

222
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:47,720
apologize.

223
00:08:49,270 --> 00:08:50,030
Second,

224
00:08:50,710 --> 00:08:51,910
we fight one-on-one.

225
00:08:53,190 --> 00:08:54,030
Babao.

226
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:57,230
Here.

227
00:08:57,610 --> 00:08:58,240
Come here.

228
00:08:58,310 --> 00:09:00,830
What are you doing?

229
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:02,710
We fight one-on-one,

230
00:09:02,710 --> 00:09:03,470
what does it have to do with

231
00:09:03,470 --> 00:09:05,330
other people? I mean, other dogs.

232
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,200
Ask the dog to leave first.

233
00:09:15,860 --> 00:09:16,920
Do you not dare?

234
00:09:17,780 --> 00:09:19,380
Apologize if you don't dare.

235
00:09:25,070 --> 00:09:25,800
One-on-one.

236
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:31,430
Why are you here?

237
00:09:33,750 --> 00:09:35,100
You left right away after school.

238
00:09:35,100 --> 00:09:36,260
I know you well.

239
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:37,050
Go ahead.

240
00:09:37,580 --> 00:09:40,040
I'll take you to the hospital if you're hurt.

241
00:09:41,710 --> 00:09:42,310
Okay.

242
00:09:42,900 --> 00:09:43,590
Today, for the sake

243
00:09:43,590 --> 00:09:44,790
of the girl pleading for you,

244
00:09:44,790 --> 00:09:45,990
I'll spare your life.

245
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,300
Keep a low profile in No. 2 High School in the future.

246
00:09:48,300 --> 00:09:50,230
You won't be so lucky in the future.

247
00:09:57,790 --> 00:09:58,760
Babao, come on.

248
00:10:02,470 --> 00:10:03,470
No more fighting?

249
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,230
Mr. Gao said

250
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,530
fighting won't solve the problem.

251
00:10:09,430 --> 00:10:10,980
But it won't be over.

252
00:10:11,350 --> 00:10:11,900
He bullied you,

253
00:10:11,900 --> 00:10:13,180
that means he's provoking me.

254
00:10:13,180 --> 00:10:15,840
No one is gonna lay a finger on you while I'm here.

255
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:18,760
It's not fair to take a dog along with him.

256
00:10:18,760 --> 00:10:20,220
He brought a helper today.

257
00:10:20,790 --> 00:10:22,310
Your disadvantage is you don't have a dog.

258
00:10:22,310 --> 00:10:22,800
Fine.

259
00:10:22,910 --> 00:10:24,630
Next time, I'll bring you the two large dogs

260
00:10:24,630 --> 00:10:25,390
in the yard.

261
00:10:25,390 --> 00:10:27,310
Two. We'll win for sure, okay?

262
00:10:27,390 --> 00:10:29,190
Don't mention those two dogs.

263
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:31,620
Those two dogs have become fat like pigs.

264
00:10:32,070 --> 00:10:33,670
Let's go home and eat Big Plate Chicken.

265
00:10:33,670 --> 00:10:35,000
What Big Plate Chicken?

266
00:10:35,290 --> 00:10:36,720
I have to keep an eye on Cheng Yaya.

267
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:37,270
None of you

268
00:10:37,270 --> 00:10:38,630
can put me at ease.

269
00:10:38,630 --> 00:10:39,950
No one won in a fight.

270
00:10:39,950 --> 00:10:40,750
Why do you say that?

271
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:41,350
Did you win?

272
00:10:41,350 --> 00:10:42,350
He ambushed me.

273
00:10:43,970 --> 00:10:45,940
[Video Arcade]

274
00:10:50,270 --> 00:10:51,910
Boss, I want a bottle of soda.

275
00:10:58,270 --> 00:10:58,950
One more.

276
00:11:08,350 --> 00:11:09,150
Daguo.

277
00:11:09,190 --> 00:11:10,120
Good for you.

278
00:11:10,140 --> 00:11:11,070
You didn't go home after school

279
00:11:11,070 --> 00:11:12,040
but played video games here.

280
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:13,510
Does your dad know about it?

281
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:14,350
I'll go back in a while.

282
00:11:14,350 --> 00:11:15,350
Don't tell my dad.

283
00:11:16,010 --> 00:11:16,690
I won't.

284
00:11:17,270 --> 00:11:18,030
I'm on night duty tonight,

285
00:11:18,030 --> 00:11:19,030
but I haven't gone yet.

286
00:11:19,030 --> 00:11:20,230
If your dad finds out,

287
00:11:20,310 --> 00:11:21,310
I'll be scolded.

288
00:11:21,590 --> 00:11:23,030
Let's play together.

289
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,000
Have fun.

290
00:11:24,660 --> 00:11:25,660
I'll play inside.

291
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:28,360
