00:22:18,110 --> 00:22:18,470
Stop it.

582
00:22:18,470 --> 00:22:18,990
Am I not a human?

583
00:22:18,990 --> 00:22:20,080
I'm a living person here.

584
00:22:20,080 --> 00:22:21,210
If we have a problem,

585
00:22:21,390 --> 00:22:22,790
let's fix it, okay?

586
00:22:22,790 --> 00:22:23,790
If we can't fix it,

587
00:22:23,790 --> 00:22:25,640
call the police, right?

588
00:22:25,640 --> 00:22:26,590
Let them handle it.

589
00:22:26,590 --> 00:22:27,960
Both of you are fine, aren't you?

590
00:22:27,960 --> 00:22:28,790
What's all the fuss about?

591
00:22:28,790 --> 00:22:29,950
You're even blocking the road.

592
00:22:29,950 --> 00:22:30,990
Dismiss, guys.

593
00:22:30,990 --> 00:22:32,190
Everything is okay.

594
00:22:32,200 --> 00:22:33,550
-He's fine.
-Pengfei.

595
00:22:33,550 --> 00:22:34,550
I'm not fine.

596
00:22:34,910 --> 00:22:35,720
What's wrong?

597
00:22:35,720 --> 00:22:36,750
My head hit the glass.

598
00:22:36,750 --> 00:22:37,630
I feel dizzy.

599
00:22:37,710 --> 00:22:38,510
My limbs are weak.

600
00:22:38,510 --> 00:22:39,310
Really.

601
00:22:39,310 --> 00:22:40,070
I feel dizzy.

602
00:22:40,070 --> 00:22:40,630
Are you okay?

603
00:22:40,630 --> 00:22:42,190
I want a full body check-up.

604
00:22:42,190 --> 00:22:42,880
Listen.

605
00:22:42,900 --> 00:22:43,510
My brother-in-law

606
00:22:43,510 --> 00:22:44,660
is the director of the staff hospital.

607
00:22:44,660 --> 00:22:45,870
You're in big trouble today.

608
00:22:45,870 --> 00:22:46,270
No, no.

609
00:22:46,270 --> 00:22:47,510
I'm not the director.

610
00:22:47,510 --> 00:22:48,670
You're a director, though you're an alternate.

611
00:22:48,670 --> 00:22:49,510
Anyway, you knocked down

612
00:22:49,510 --> 00:22:50,390
a director's family member today.

613
00:22:50,390 --> 00:22:51,950
Just wait and see.

614
00:22:51,950 --> 00:22:53,070
Zhang, go to the hospital. Hurry up.

615
00:22:53,070 --> 00:22:54,000
Just wait.

616
00:23:07,130 --> 00:23:08,060
What do you want?

617
00:23:09,260 --> 00:23:11,520
I'll dump the garbage. You mop the floor.

618
00:23:44,330 --> 00:23:45,390
What are you doing?

619
00:23:45,720 --> 00:23:46,910
You always leave without a word.

620
00:23:46,910 --> 00:23:48,310
Do you think you're cool?

621
00:23:48,550 --> 00:23:50,550
Who doesn't know how to play it cool?

622
00:24:09,130 --> 00:24:09,930
Fight with me?

623
00:24:10,490 --> 00:24:12,090
You've got the wrong person.

624
00:24:15,230 --> 00:24:15,830
Hit me?

625
00:24:16,830 --> 00:24:17,790
Baoshan.

626
00:24:18,660 --> 00:24:19,860
You hit your head?

627
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:21,200
Is it serious?

628
00:24:21,630 --> 00:24:22,820
Are there any other parts you got hurt?

629
00:24:22,820 --> 00:24:23,950
Just a little dizzy.

630
00:24:24,670 --> 00:24:26,190
Have you taken a CT scan?

631
00:24:26,270 --> 00:24:27,850
Where is your brother-in-law?

632
00:24:27,850 --> 00:24:28,580
Here.

633
00:24:29,230 --> 00:24:30,720
I went to buy noodles for him.

634
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:31,430
Look at him, he's severely injured.

635
00:24:31,430 --> 00:24:32,470
Did you take a CT scan for him?

636
00:24:32,470 --> 00:24:33,070
Look.

637
00:24:33,070 --> 00:24:33,910
Look at how hurt he is.

638
00:24:33,910 --> 00:24:34,710
What's so serious?

639
00:24:34,710 --> 00:24:36,030
He even asked for two bowls of noodles.

640
00:24:36,030 --> 00:24:37,670
I haven't had the second bowl yet.

641
00:24:37,670 --> 00:24:39,390
Pengfei, the noodles are a bit salty.

642
00:24:39,390 --> 00:24:40,060
There's not much meat.

643
00:24:40,060 --> 00:24:40,870
Uncle Tian's cooking

644
00:24:40,870 --> 00:24:41,800
is not as good as before.

645
00:24:41,800 --> 00:24:42,480
Fine.

646
00:24:42,710 --> 00:24:44,230
I'll go to Uncle Tian later

647
00:24:44,270 --> 00:24:45,620
and tell him what you said.

648
00:24:45,620 --> 00:24:46,890
-Don't.
-See if he cooks noodles for you

649
00:24:46,890 --> 00:24:48,220
when he comes next time.

650
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:50,060
It affects our relationship.

651
00:24:50,370 --> 00:24:50,890
Wait, your head

652
00:24:50,890 --> 00:24:52,010
wasn't injured.

653
00:24:52,100 --> 00:24:53,650
Who wrapped this for you?

654
00:24:54,760 --> 00:24:56,890
I'm doing this to be seen by the driver.

655
00:24:57,190 --> 00:24:57,710
You...

656
00:24:58,050 --> 00:24:58,670
Yu.

657
00:24:58,670 --> 00:25:00,550
You scared me.

658
00:25:00,700 --> 00:25:03,160
I thought it was a very serious car accident.

659
00:25:03,580 --> 00:25:04,450
For goodness' sake.

660
00:25:04,450 --> 00:25:05,390
When I got the call,

661
00:25:05,390 --> 00:25:07,110
I was so scared that my legs were weak.

662
00:25:07,110 --> 00:25:08,660
My hands were sweaty.

663
00:25:09,810 --> 00:25:11,510
Yu, I'm blessed.

664
00:25:11,510 --> 00:25:12,630
What could happen to me?

665
00:25:12,630 --> 00:25:14,340
Did you forget that it rained for a week

666
00:25:14,340 --> 00:25:16,320
before our mom gave birth to me?

667
00:25:16,430 --> 00:25:17,430
After I was born,

668
00:25:17,460 --> 00:25:18,230
the sky turned clear,

669
00:25:18,230 --> 00:25:19,290
and a big rainbow

670
00:25:19,310 --> 00:25:20,260
appeared in the sky

671
00:25:20,260 --> 00:25:21,420
to welcome me.

672
00:25:21,440 --> 00:25:23,050
Pengfei, what kind of life do you think I've got?

673
00:25:23,050 --> 00:25:24,290
You're a bandit.

674
00:25:25,920 --> 00:25:28,050
You've been troublesome since young.

675
00:25:28,180 --> 00:25:29,660
So unreliable.

676
00:25:29,760 --> 00:25:31,160
Don't come here anymore.

677
00:25:31,310 --> 00:25:32,880
Yu, you have no conscience.

678
00:25:32,950 --> 00:25:33,670
If it weren't for you,

679
00:25:33,670 --> 00:25:35,180
I wouldn't have suffered like this.

680
00:25:35,180 --> 00:25:36,550
Mom thinks about you all the time.

681
00:25:36,550 --> 00:25:37,270
Every time she has something nice,

682
00:25:37,270 --> 00:25:38,440
she asks me to deliver it to you.

683
00:25:38,440 --> 00:25:40,050
As if you have a conscience.

684
00:25:40,080 --> 00:25:41,860
You're over 30, but you're still not married.

685
00:25:41,860 --> 00:25:42,870
You just stay at home

686
00:25:42,870 --> 00:25:44,210
and live off your parents.

687
00:25:44,210 --> 00:25:45,010
You have spent

688
00:25:45,010 --> 00:25:46,410
all your parents' money.

689
00:25:46,810 --> 00:25:47,880
A true man

690
00:25:48,140 --> 00:25:49,470
should be ambitious

691
00:25:49,490 --> 00:25:50,920
and not always be immersed in love.

692
00:25:50,920 --> 00:25:51,420
Right?

693
00:25:51,450 --> 00:25:52,970
If I get married early,

694
00:25:53,080 --> 00:25:54,320
how can I build my career?

695
00:25:54,320 --> 00:25:56,480
What kind of career do you have?

696
00:25:56,500 --> 00:25:57,220
You...

697
00:25:57,900 --> 00:25:58,830
At your age,

698
00:25:58,830 --> 00:26:00,690
you'd better have some romances.

699
00:26:00,750 --> 00:26:01,550
Don't end up in a situation where Mom and Dad

700
00:26:01,550 --> 00:26:02,590
can't even see your children.

701
00:26:02,590 --> 00:26:04,430
Don't say that. How depressing.

702
00:26:04,840 --> 00:26:06,440
I'm waiting for my true love.

703
00:26:06,660 --> 00:26:07,380
By the way, Yu,

704
00:26:07,380 --> 00:26:08,430
don't tell Mom

705
00:26:08,430 --> 00:26:09,480
about the accident.

706
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:10,880
I don't want her to worry.

707
00:26:11,560 --> 00:26:12,540
Am I that crazy

708
00:26:12,540 --> 00:26:13,890
to tell her that?

709
00:26:14,080 --> 00:26:15,670
You look fine to me after all.

710
00:26:15,670 --> 00:26:16,770
Why are you hospitalized?

711
00:26:16,770 --> 00:26:17,990
Do you have a lot of money?

712
00:26:17,990 --> 00:26:19,450
Did you arrange it for him?

713
00:26:20,910 --> 00:26:21,460
No.

714
00:26:22,180 --> 00:26:24,520
He asked to be hospitalized for a check-up.

715
00:26:24,520 --> 00:26:25,870
Isn't he your brother?

716
00:26:26,550 --> 00:26:27,270
I did it to

717
00:26:27,270 --> 00:26:28,590
punish the driver.

718
00:26:28,590 --> 00:26:29,850
Right? So he won't be that careless next time.

719
00:26:29,850 --> 00:26:31,850
Wait, he has to pay the hospital fee.

720
00:26:32,390 --> 00:26:32,990
The flowers are obviously...

721
00:26:32,990 --> 00:26:33,550
Pengfei, where is Zhang?

722
00:26:33,550 --> 00:26:34,510
...short of potassium.

723
00:26:34,510 --> 00:26:35,580
He is in discussions with the driver's workplace

724
00:26:35,580 --> 00:26:37,630
about compensation for the repairs.

725
00:26:37,630 --> 00:26:38,240
Good.

726
00:26:39,670 --> 00:26:41,870
At first, I was going to leave tomorrow.

727
00:26:41,980 --> 00:26:42,840
But it'll take a few days

728
00:26:42,840 --> 00:26:44,030
to fix the car.

729
00:26:44,060 --> 00:26:45,150
I plan to have a thorough check-up

730
00:26:45,150 --> 00:26:46,150
in the hospital.

731
00:26:46,540 --> 00:26:47,340
By the way, Yu,

732
00:26:47,820 --> 00:26:48,620
my heart

733
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:50,320
has been beating fast lately.

734
00:26:50,710 --> 00:26:51,520
Did I inherit

735
00:26:51,550 --> 00:26:52,830
Dad's heart disease?

736
00:26:53,870 --> 00:26:54,870
Dad's heart disease

737
00:26:54,870 --> 00:26:55,870
is because of you.

738
00:26:56,060 --> 00:26:58,860
You should pack up and leave the hospital quickly.

739
00:26:59,420 --> 00:27:00,720
Not only does he not work hard,

740
00:27:00,720 --> 00:27:02,590
but he also has something wrong with his brain.

741
00:27:02,590 --> 00:27:04,380
Is he dumb or deaf?

742
00:27:04,650 --> 00:27:06,370
He doesn't answer me when I talk to him.

743
00:27:06,370 --> 00:27:07,350
It's like someone owes him.

744
00:27:07,350 --> 00:27:08,680
I'm so annoyed with him.

745
00:27:09,360 --> 00:27:10,870
He's annoyed with you too.

746
00:27:10,900 --> 00:27:11,760
Annoyed with me?

747
00:27:11,760 --> 00:27:13,040
He's jealous of me.

748
00:27:17,030 --> 00:27:17,430
No way.

749
00:27:17,460 --> 00:27:19,260
I get angry when I talk about him.

750
00:27:19,800 --> 00:27:20,720
It's so late.

751
00:27:21,210 --> 00:27:22,830
Why aren't your parents back yet?

752
00:27:22,830 --> 00:27:23,550
What happened?

753
00:27:23,550 --> 00:27:24,230
Yaya's not back too.

754
00:27:24,230 --> 00:27:25,360
What's wrong with your family?

755
00:27:25,360 --> 00:27:26,090
I don't know.

756
00:27:27,440 --> 00:27:28,140
Auntie.

757
00:27:28,470 --> 00:27:29,470
Li Si.

758
00:27:35,540 --> 00:27:36,580
You went too far.

759
00:27:36,620 --> 00:27:37,630
Do you still care about this family

760
00:27:37,630 --> 00:27:38,610
and your children?

761
00:27:38,610 --> 00:27:39,140
Here.

762
00:27:39,160 --> 00:27:39,840
No.

763
00:27:40,430 --> 00:27:41,360
Drinking soda again?

764
00:27:41,360 --> 00:27:42,600
It was me.

765
00:27:42,630 --> 00:27:43,440
I opened it.

766
00:27:43,460 --> 00:27:45,170
Miaomiao.

767
00:27:45,350 --> 00:27:47,670
-Uncle.
-Uncle.

768
00:27:48,470 --> 00:27:49,810
How long have you been back?

769
00:27:49,810 --> 00:27:50,740
Where did you go?

770
00:27:50,760 --> 00:27:52,700
I was handling something with your parents.

771
00:27:52,700 --> 00:27:54,560
Mr. Si, you're still so handsome.

772
00:27:54,590 --> 00:27:55,390
Stop calling me Mr. Si.

773
00:27:55,390 --> 00:27:56,390
You're my elder.

774
00:27:56,680 --> 00:27:57,350
How energetic.

775
00:27:57,350 --> 00:27:57,750
Uncle.

776
00:27:58,110 --> 00:27:59,330
You two haven't eaten yet?

777
00:27:59,330 --> 00:28:00,630
What can we eat? Where can we eat?

778
00:28:00,630 --> 00:28:01,930
You don't even come back to cook after work.

779
00:28:01,930 --> 00:28:02,830
You're so lazy.

780
00:28:02,830 --> 00:28:04,760
There's everything in the fridge.

781
00:28:04,830 --> 00:28:05,670
You won't starve to death

782
00:28:05,670 --> 00:28:06,590
even if you only eat the biscuits.

783
00:28:06,590 --> 00:28:07,190
No.

784
00:28:07,280 --> 00:28:08,670
Let's go out and eat.

785
00:28:08,670 --> 00:28:09,350
-Pengfei.
-Okay.

786
00:28:09,350 --> 00:28:10,460
Is it your treat?

787
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:12,080
We'll eat out if you treat us.

788
00:28:12,730 --> 00:28:13,330
Well,

789
00:28:13,680 --> 00:28:14,670
the restaurants outside

790
00:28:14,670 --> 00:28:15,650
are not very hygienic.

791
00:28:15,650 --> 00:28:16,650
Let's eat at home.

792
00:28:16,760 --> 00:28:18,620
My mom's restaurant is hygienic.

793
00:28:22,480 --> 00:28:23,350
Where is Yaya?

794
00:28:23,380 --> 00:28:24,220
Yaya?

795
00:28:24,470 --> 00:28:27,190
I think Yaya went to rob a grave.

796
00:28:27,220 --> 00:28:28,200
To rob a grave.

797
00:28:28,880 --> 00:28:29,850
Uncle, look.

798
00:28:29,910 --> 00:28:30,990
He doesn't care about you.

799
00:28:30,990 --> 00:28:32,310
He doesn't love you.

800
00:28:32,310 --> 00:28:33,230
I can see that.

801
00:28:33,230 --> 00:28:34,880
But it doesn't stop me from loving him.

802
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:35,520
No.

803
00:28:35,760 --> 00:28:37,440
I love you the most, Miaomiao.

804
00:28:37,990 --> 00:28:38,910
What about me?

805
00:28:40,080 --> 00:28:41,610
Second, you're the second.

806
00:28:42,270 --> 00:28:43,140
By the way, Yu,

807
00:28:43,270 --> 00:28:44,630
the stuff Mom gave you

808
00:28:44,630 --> 00:28:45,550
is in the car.

809
00:28:45,780 --> 00:28:46,380
Li Si.

810
00:28:46,710 --> 00:28:47,240
Let's go.

811
00:28:47,260 --> 00:28:47,810
Go.

812
00:28:48,540 --> 00:28:49,490
You guys cook.

813
00:28:50,120 --> 00:28:51,160
I'll be back soon.

814
00:28:53,300 --> 00:28:54,090
Uncle,

815
00:28:54,670 --> 00:28:55,230
why do you bring

816
00:28:55,230 --> 00:28:55,750
so many things

817
00:28:55,750 --> 00:28:57,210
and tire me out every time?

818
00:28:57,550 --> 00:28:58,620
Aren't you young?

819
00:28:59,560 --> 00:29:02,220
It's all about a mother's love for her daughter.

820
00:29:02,650 --> 00:29:04,350
How long are you going to stay this time?

821
00:29:04,350 --> 00:29:05,540
I was going to leave tomorrow.

822
00:29:05,540 --> 00:29:06,480
But the car broke down.

823
00:29:06,480 --> 00:29:07,850
So I'll wait until the car is fixed.

824
00:29:07,850 --> 00:29:09,780
We can spend the weekend together.

825
00:29:10,010 --> 00:29:11,210
What's fun recently?

826
00:29:11,510 --> 00:29:13,270
The arcade near

827
00:29:13,270 --> 00:29:14,830
the farmers' market has been renovated.

828
00:29:14,830 --> 00:29:16,110
A few game machines are added.

829
00:29:16,110 --> 00:29:16,760
It's really fun.

830
00:29:16,760 --> 00:29:18,960
There's also a barbecue shop. Amazing.

831
00:29:19,270 --> 00:29:21,210
Then let's have some fun as brothers this weekend.

832
00:29:21,210 --> 00:29:22,820
No, as uncle and nephew.

833
00:29:25,120 --> 00:29:25,800
Uncle.

834
00:29:27,850 --> 00:29:28,680
And there's another interesting one.

835
00:29:28,680 --> 00:29:29,760
Don't tell others.

836
00:29:30,700 --> 00:29:31,290
What?

837
00:29:34,650 --> 00:29:36,290
I'm good at this.

838
00:29:36,310 --> 00:29:37,190
Really?

839
00:29:38,630 --> 00:29:39,860
As for the movie played by Chow Yun-fat

840
00:29:39,860 --> 00:29:40,660
in Hong Kong,

841
00:29:40,680 --> 00:29:41,980
where he has a slicked-back hairstyle,

842
00:29:41,980 --> 00:29:43,390
I'm the original model.

843
00:29:43,670 --> 00:29:45,110
Are you so talented?

844
00:29:45,110 --> 00:29:46,590
Of course, I'm your uncle.

845
00:29:47,750 --> 00:29:48,650
Let's do it tomorrow.

846
00:29:48,650 --> 00:29:49,520
Let's do it.

847
00:29:50,180 --> 00:29:50,980
Move forward.

848
00:30:00,400 --> 00:30:01,510
Come on.

849
00:30:02,260 --> 00:30:03,500
You scared me.

850
00:30:04,110 --> 00:30:05,390
Drink some honey water

851
00:30:05,390 --> 00:30:06,050
to sober up.

852
00:30:06,060 --> 00:30:07,980
I don't want to drink that.

853
00:30:24,550 --> 00:30:25,710
It's just a matter of drinking honey water.

854
00:30:25,710 --> 00:30:26,910
What's with the bang?

855
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:29,000
There are no outsiders here.

856
00:30:31,810 --> 00:30:32,580
How is it?

857
00:30:33,530 --> 00:30:34,520
How is it?

858
00:30:34,550 --> 00:30:35,390
Is there a place available

859
00:30:35,390 --> 00:30:36,590
at the agency?

860
00:30:36,950 --> 00:30:37,550
Yes.

861
00:30:38,470 --> 00:30:39,710
I told you

862
00:30:39,710 --> 00:30:41,310
I had the right information.

863
00:30:42,190 --> 00:30:43,320
Can you fight for it?

864
00:30:45,080 --> 00:30:45,800
Not really.

865
00:30:46,910 --> 00:30:47,830
There is only one place left.

866
00:30:47,830 --> 00:30:49,830
But so many executives are waiting.

867
00:30:50,170 --> 00:30:51,960
Isn't that bullshit?

